<BaseLayout title="About - Domain Discoverer" description="Discover valuable domain names faster. We provide availability checks, curated tools, and practical guides for investors, businesses, SaaS, SEO experts, and startups.">
  <section class="container-pad"> 
    <article class="prose">
      <h1>About Domain Discoverer</h1>
      <p>DomainDiscoverer.com helps you uncover valuable domain names quickly and confidently. We focus on speed, clarity, and practical workflows. Our guides and tools are built for domain investors and anyone who needs a strong name: business owners, SaaS teams, SEO experts, and startups.</p>

      <h2>What We Do</h2>
      <p>We combine instant availability checks, high‑leverage research tools, and hands‑on guidance. The goal is to reduce guesswork and help you decide faster.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Instant checks to confirm domain availability</li>
        <li>Guides that explain how to evaluate names</li>
        <li>Curated tools that speed up research</li>
        <li>Practical examples and repeatable workflows</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Who It’s For</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Domain investors who want fast, reliable triage</li>
        <li>Founders and product teams naming a new venture</li>
        <li>SEO professionals validating search and link signals</li>
        <li>Marketers testing positioning and brand options</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>How We Evaluate Domains</h2>
      <p>Our content emphasizes factors that consistently correlate with value and usability:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Brandability</strong> — clear, memorable, and pronounceable</li>
        <li><strong>Signals</strong> — search demand, backlinks, and footprints</li>
        <li><strong>Risk</strong> — potential confusion, trademarks, and ambiguity</li>
        <li><strong>Liquidity</strong> — comps, niches, and resale dynamics</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>How We Choose Tools</h2>
      <p>Tools highlighted on the site are selected for real‑world usefulness:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Clear value for finding and evaluating names</li>
        <li>Transparent pricing and data sources</li>
        <li>Strong track record in the domaining community</li>
        <li>Good learning curve for beginners and pros</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Professional Standards</h2>
      <p>We don’t sell personal data. We only send email to people who ask to receive it; every message includes an unsubscribe link or clear directions to opt out. We keep cookies simple and only use what’s needed for the site to function.</p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>Questions or feedback are welcome. Please reach out via our <a href="/contact">contact page</a>.</p>
    </article>

